snippet.title: Critter Cove - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX | Kinda Funny Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Take another look at Critter Cove in this latest trailer for the open-world life sim and town-building game set in a cozy post-apocalyptic paradise. The trailer showcases some of the features you can expect from Critter Cove, like rebuilding the island town to attract tourists, tourism activities, and how you can personalize your island. Critter Cove will be available on PC, PlayStation, and Xbox. In Critter Cove, restore an old town, sail across a mysterious archipelago, hunt relics and farm, fish & craft everything you need. Can you help turn Critter Cove into a thriving tourist town once again?
